      <title>大修后，南非通货膨胀会加速</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/south-african-inflation-accelerates-after-data-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[统计局修订了用于计算家庭支出的数据后，南非通货膨胀加速了，这使决策者有理由在下个月降低利率谨慎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/south-african-inflation-accelerates-after-data-overhaul</guid>
